NPCName "Ken Neff"
Location "Bottom Floor of Vault 31, Board Room"
Description "Ken Neff is the one that gives the PC the quest to go grab the Mr. Handy OS. However, nothing the PC says gets passed on to the CEO, in true corporate fashion. Also, when the PC returns, Ken Neff just gives him a floater saying \"Go see Mr. Bergandi.\""
Unknown_Desc "A older man, possibly in his early 50's."
Known_Desc "Ken Neff, Vice President of Customer Solutions."
Detailed_Desc "Although he is older, this man is in excellent shape. He looks well fed and rested, much like the other Board members."
/* Regular nodes */

Node "Start"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[He looks up from the stack of papers he is reading.] This had better be important. I'm a VERY busy man."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Are you Ken Neff?" linkto "A1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I was told to report to the Board." linkto "A2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry to bother you. I'll be going now" linkto "done"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Me <PC>. You Ken?" linkto "A1"  notes ""
          int=-3 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Sorry Mr. Busy. I let you work." linkto "done"  notes ""
              }
}
