Node "B3"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "[He chuckles] How very... uncouth of you. Very well, I'll explain why we summoned you. What do you know about the reactor?"
      options {
          int=6 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wattz special model 1372-E, specially modified by the Wattz corporation to meet the power requirements of this Vault. It uses weapons-grade fuel for increased efficiency, and is currently being maintained by the MR. \nHandies." linkto "E1"  notes ""
          int=5 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "I know that it's been maintained by Mr. Handy Robots for several years now. I also know that Mr. Handy was not designed to maintain fusion reactors." linkto "E2"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Just the basics - its a fusion reactor and it powers this Vault." linkto "E3"  notes ""
              }
}
Node "C2"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Sir? [He smiles] What a pleasant surprise. It's nice to see that at least some of the technicians demonstrate proper respect. You'll have to excuse me but quite a few of you have decidedly... distasteful vocabularies."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "With all due respect, that seems beside the point." linkto "C4"  notes ""
              }
}
