          int=5 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Well, you had the Mr. Handies reprogrammed to run the coolant system. Is there something wrong with them?" linkto "E2-1" conditions { CHECK_SKILL science >= 20 link_next NONE } notes ""
