Node "Want1"
notes ""
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "Although we have no way of knowing what state the G.A.I. building is in, we need someone to go out and search for it. The Mr. Handy OS is vital to the survival of this Vault. You are the candidate best suited for this job. You have demonstrated initiative, critical thinking skills, and leadership potential."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Thank you sir, I -" linkto "Team1"  notes ""
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "Wait. Stop right there. I'm not going." linkto "Refusal1"  notes "This option should appear if the player notices the notes in node G2."
              }
}
Node "End1"
notes "PC should receive equipment withdrawal forms here."
is_wtg = false
{
NPCText "I'm glad to see you're confident about this. Take these forms to the Quartermaster, she will give you supplies for the voyage. Don't forget - the fate of this Vault rests in your hands. Whether we live or die is up to you. Godspeed, <PC>."
      options {
          int=4 Reaction=REACTION_NEUTRAL playertext "[End.]" linkto "done"  notes "Quest accepted. Add the Vault quest to the Pipboy."
              }
}
